client.interfaces

Interface IUi

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BranchManagerUI, CancelAppointmentUI, ClientHistoryUI, CreateAppointmentUI, CreateClientUI, CreateExaminationUI, CreateLabReferenceUI, DispatcherUI, GeneralManagerUI, LabWorkerUI, LoginUI, RecordAppointmentUI, SpecialistUI, TransferDetailsUI, TransferTableUI, ViewAppointmentRecordUI, ViewExaminationUI, ViewReferenceUI

    public interface IUi
    An interface that used to collect all the GUI instances. Used in the GUI elements stack in the main application. Helps to handle the views. Helps to get control on the user operations. Helps to handle window switching.
    Author:
    shays
